<div class="title">Intense Visuals</div>
<div class="substance">2C-B & Mefloquine</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Fuzz&Exact=1">Fuzz</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Fuzz. "Intense Visuals: An Experience with 2C-B & Mefloquine (exp98806)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Apr 10, 2013. erowid.org/exp/98806</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
